      <title>矿业利润下滑 中国顶级煤炭企业纷纷转向电力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/china-s-top-coal-firms-lean-into-power-as-mining-profits-slip</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着燃料价格下降以及电气化成为中国低碳转型的中心，中国顶级煤炭生产商正在加速进军发电领域。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/china-s-top-coal-firms-lean-into-power-as-mining-profits-slip</guid>
